trans-unit.source: Specifies visibility of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"></xref> move handle (grip).
trans-unit.target: Anger synligheten på en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"> </xref> Flytta handtaget (greppet).

trans-unit.source: In a stack layout, make a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip> movable by putting it in a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripPanel> and ensuring that its <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.GripStyle%2A> is set to Visible.
trans-unit.target: I en stack-layout, se en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>rörliga genom att placera den i en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripPanel>och se till att dess <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.GripStyle%2A>har angetts till Visible.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.GripStyle%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripPanel> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>

trans-unit.source: Specifies that a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"></xref> move handle (grip) is not visible.
trans-unit.target: Anger att en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"> </xref> flytta referensen (greppet) inte är synlig.

trans-unit.source: Specifies that a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"></xref> move handle (grip) is visible.
trans-unit.target: Anger att en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"> </xref> flytta referensen (greppet) visas.
